Title: Peak XV Partners sells 1.5 pc stake in MobiKwik for Rs 82 cr
Summary: Peak XV Partners (formerly Sequoia India) sold 1.5% stake in MobiKwik for Rs 82 crore, reducing its holding to 1.26%, while MobiKwik's shares rose 2.40% following its recent successful IPO.
